{"tid":1626364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"手足快啲懲罰深水埗呢間舖頭！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:41.000Z","uid":220685,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"69c195585902750d52e1b71c90c98622913d2407","tid":1626364,"uid":220685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBWv36p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBWv36p.jpg&h=372a8792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說老母去呢間舖買公仔，佢返嚟俾張收據我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足一齊大大力懲罰呢間舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b6ad7bb62c8b8e5d31b8f7f9c596170b35f3b2","tid":1626364,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"1e4ba1fef1dc81c7eef5ac89464a3d5ec7f684bd","tid":1626364,"uid":220685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e64f7860934031c5a589d47898cb38c67529c49d","tid":1626364,"uid":220685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T21:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4db1c6f08996a13bb132ea4b5adcb9b1eaa1885